---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro'
const lastUpdated = '2026-06-10'
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Pilot.BM terms of service."
>
  <section style="background-color: var(--color-sand); padding-block: var(--space-10);">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: var(--text-3xl);">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--color-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm);">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container" style="padding-block: var(--space-12);">
    <div style="max-width: 720px;" class="prose">

      <h2>1. Acceptance of terms</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing or using Pilot.BM ("the Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.
        If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Site.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Informational purpose only</h2>
      <p>
        The content on Pilot.BM is provided for general informational and educational purposes only.
        Nothing on this Site constitutes legal, immigration, tax, financial, or professional advice.
        You should not act on any information on this Site without first consulting a qualified professional.
      </p>
      <p>
        Regulations, fees, and policies referenced on this Site may change. Always verify current
        requirements at authoritative sources including <a href="https://www.gov.bm" rel="noopener" target="_blank">gov.bm</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>3. No warranties</h2>
      <p>
        The Site is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied.
        Pilot.BM does not warrant that information is accurate, complete, or current.
        We make no representations about the suitability of information for any purpose.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, Pilot.BM and its operators shall not be liable for
        any direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or exemplary damages arising from
        your use of this Site or reliance on its content.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Affiliate links</h2>
      <p>
        Some links on this Site are affiliate links. We may receive a commission if you make a purchase
        through these links. See our <a href="/legal/affiliate-disclosure">affiliate disclosure</a> for details.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        All original content on Pilot.BM is the property of Pilot.BM and may not be reproduced without
        written permission. Factual information (laws, regulations, publicly available data) is not
        protected by copyright.
      </p>

      <h2>7. External links</h2>
      <p>
        Links to third-party sites are provided for convenience. Pilot.BM has no control over and
        takes no responsibility for the content of external sites.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Governing law</h2>
      <p>
        These terms are governed by the laws of the jurisdiction in which the operator is located.
        Any disputes shall be resolved in that jurisdiction.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to update these Terms at any time. Continued use of the Site after
        changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms: <a href="mailto:matt@ravenpower.net">matt@ravenpower.net</a>
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
